observations.recommendation:
We recommend that the management require:
                                                        a. the Planning and Development Council to judiciously and meticulously plan projects/ programs/ activities (PPAs) to be included in the Local Development Plan and Annual Investment Plan indicating in  details   specific PPAs embodied therein and promptly implement PPAs embodied in the 20% LDF in order to optimize the delivery of basic services to the people;

    b. the officers/personnel concerned to conduct in-depth analysis and ensure that Program of Works (POW) have been prepared in order to ascertain a more realistic estimates of work items and costs as basis in appropriating fund thereof.

